Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Small car sales boom
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w4qb
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Sep 1980
US car makers to concentrate on making smaller cars as sale of thrifty foreign imports boom. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less